{"tid":55160,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有車牌想補鐘練泊車","createTime":"2016-12-26T07:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T09:50:12.000Z","uid":31194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af451668597c6dbe62b310d018d8055deb28d57b","tid":55160,"uid":31194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T07:32:01.000Z","msg":"本身已經拎咗車牌3-4年，之前有半年係外國揸車，因為啲路同車位夠闊所以都乜問題，但返到黎香港因爲泊車唔叻所以有啲恐懼一直唔敢揸。<br />\n<br />\n想問下各位有無師傅係集中補鐘補泊車既介紹下？駕院係咪好貴又唔抵？"},{"pid":"c663bee3a317bcb7fcfa4ff802c0d674f6dd04f0","tid":55160,"uid":858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T07:37:19.000Z","msg":"香港有車的話 自己練都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a90ff4a72065ed60452b9721974d0aafc6b56d4","tid":55160,"uid":31194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T07:39:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港有車的話 自己練都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為屋企人都唔識揸，所以一個人揸完全無信心就一直無買車，啲停車場又窄。整花自己架車唔緊要，最驚撞花人地"},{"pid":"354959a6a527ee8d4a6d311265899762b5881053","tid":55160,"uid":858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T07:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港有車的話 自己練都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為屋企人都唔識揸，所以一個人揸完全無信心就一直無買車，啲停車場又窄。整花自己架車唔緊要，最驚撞花人地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去遠啲地方嘅街標練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱練梗係唔會喺停車場練啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9574ea3c061145227a265d8c1971fd0fe154b7d6","tid":55160,"uid":2769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T07:43:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港有車的話 自己練都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為屋企人都唔識揸，所以一個人揸完全無信心就一直無買車，啲停車場又窄。整花自己架車唔緊要，最驚撞花人地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵日放假趁啲人出左車咪搵啲空位練下入線"},{"pid":"15bb8d4677294bd8e71f100e412034796a5a919e","tid":55160,"uid":21861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T09:50:12.000Z","msg":"我p牌都係咁晚上自己練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}